## 6.3 Arsitektur Backend

Gunakan modular monolith untuk MVP.

```text
API Layer
    ↓
Application Layer
    ↓
Domain Layer
    ↓
Infrastructure Layer
    ↓
Database dan External Services
```

Struktur project:

```text
src/
├── AIHelpdesk.Api
├── AIHelpdesk.Application
├── AIHelpdesk.Domain
├── AIHelpdesk.Infrastructure
└── AIHelpdesk.Contracts

tests/
